=== 新闻业 ===

* 面向消费者的游戏新闻业始于[[街机黄金时代|街机黄金时代]]《[[太空侵略者|太空侵略者]]》成功后不久，电视和纸质报章杂志上涌现大量关于电子游戏这一新兴媒体的文章<ref name="eg_2_36">{{cite journal|title=Players Guide To Electronic Science Fiction Games|journal=[[Electronic_Games|Electronic Games]]|date=March 1982|volume=1|issue=2|pages=35–45 [36]|url=http://www.archive.org/stream/electronic-games-magazine-1982-03/Electronic_Games_Issue_02_Vol_01_02_1982_Mar#page/n35/mode/1up|accessdate=1 February 2012}}</ref>。
* 北美最早的定期消费者电子游戏专栏是《[[视频_(杂志)|视频]]》的“街机巷”，由[[比尔·孔克尔|比尔·孔克尔]]和阿尼·卡茨与乔伊·斯沃利执笔<ref name="wired_kunkel">{{cite web|last=Kohler|first=Chris|title=Bill Kunkel, Original Gaming Journalist, Dies at 61|url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/09/bill-kunkel-dies/all/1|work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|accessdate=1 March 2012|date=September 6, 2011|archive-date=2014-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324173738/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/09/bill-kunkel-dies/all/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 知名发行 ==

=== 游戏 ===

; 街机
* 6月 － [[太東|太東]]在日本发行[[西角友宏|西角友宏]]的街机游戏《[[太空侵略者|太空侵略者]]》。游戏在全球的成功标志着[[街机游戏黄金时期|街机游戏黄金时期]]的到来。游戏为[[清版射击游戏|清版射击游戏]]确立了样板<ref name="1UP_50">{{cite web|title=Essential 50: Space Invaders|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|url=http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-space-invaders|accessdate=2011-03-26|archive-date=2012-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018124241/http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-space-invaders|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并影响了后来大多数[[射击游戏|射击游戏]]<ref name="1UP_10things">{{cite web| url = http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3168373| title = Ten Things Everyone Should Know About Space Invaders| publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]]| author = Edwards, Benj| accessdate = 2008-07-11| archive-date = 2009-02-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090226064943/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3168373| dead-url = no}}</ref>。
* 10月 － [[Midway|Midway]]在北美大规模发行《太空侵略者》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arcade-history.com/?page=detail&id=31739 |title=Space Invaders arcade video game by Midway Mfg. (1978)<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |access-date=2015-02-27 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026124106/https://www.arcade-history.com/?page=detail&id=31739 }}</ref>。
* 10月 － [[南梦宫|南梦宫]]在日本推出公司首款街机游戏《[[小蜜蜂_(游戏)|小蜜蜂]]》。
* [[任天堂|任天堂]]推出其首款街机游戏《[[电脑奥赛罗|电脑奥赛罗]]》。
* [[Cinematronics|Cinematronics]]发行[[矢量图形|矢量图形]]街机游戏《[[Space_Wars|Space Wars]]》。
* [[科乐美|科乐美]]推出其首款街机游戏《Block Game》。
* [[雅达利|雅达利]]通过街机游戏《足球》推广其[[轨迹球|轨迹球]]控制器。

